Requirements

  A bourne shell compatible, like bash, ash, dash, ksh, pdksh, zsh.
  
  grep
  
  sed
  
  coreutils (cat, ls)

  On ubuntu: sudo aptitude install libtool automake autoconf gcc g++ libbz2-dev libz-dev libdb4.7-dev make gawk fakeroot


Building/Script preparation

  sh setup.sh build

Installation (as root)

  sh setup.sh install --prefix=DIRECTORY
